INSTITUTION="Internet Engineering Task Force",
NUMBER=1735,
MONTH=dec,
YEAR=1994,
ABSTRACT="This document describes the NBMA Address Resolution Protocol
(NARP). NARP can be used by a source terminal (host or router) connected
